description.content:
Greetings,

This is aynulshifat, ready to serve you 24/7, at your service. I will create a high converting responsive landing page/ squeeze page from scratch with an eye-catching unique design that will surely help you in traffic conversion and boost up sales.


SERVICES:

  • WordPress or HTML Landing Page
  • Squeeze Page/ Promo Page
  • PSD to WordPress
  • Click/ Sales Funnel
  • Coming Soon or Under Construction Page
  • Convert or Clone Existing Website 
  • Hero Section with Image/ Slider/ Video
  • Opt-In/ Popup/ Signup/ Membership Form 


WHY ME?

  • Fast Delivery 
  • 24/7 Support 
  • 100% Satisfaction & Money-Back Guarantee
  • Video Guide


EXTRA: 

  • 100% Responsive
  • Mailchimp/ Social media integration
  • Woocommerce/ Payment Gateway Integration
  • Auto Responder
  • 30 Days Free Support
  • Pricing Packages
  • SEO, Security & Speed Optimization
  • Additional Features According To Your Requirements.


STATEMENT:

As each and every project is unique, please share your requirements before placing the order to complete your project.

Simply place your order and focus on your other tasks, I am here to do the rest.


Send me a message to see some of my past works!

Hope to hear from you soon.

Best Regards,



Aynulshifat

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am ready to purchase! What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You would need a domain name and a hosting account (if you don't have these I will assist you).I will also need your logo (optional), names & no. of pages, a few sentences about your website/company, e mail address to configure form, a few images from google (I will try to arrange similar ones).

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website easily? I do not know programming
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Your website will be fully editable! You will be able to very easily add text & images to all pages with a click! You will be able to edit ecommerce products, their images, descriptions & prices and add unlimited pages and posts too. No programming skills required! :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide money back guarantee?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. After completing and delivering the product, if you find it is not according to your requirements or not what you wanted, you can ask for your money back.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you able to create exact same design of link provided?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I can create exact same design of sample or link provided. Inbox me the URL of website you like.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you upload the website on my hosting to make it live?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Uploading the website to your hosting is not part of this gig. However I will be happy to do this for you as a bonus *if* you provide your Hosting Control Panel url, username and password before I begin working. If these credentials are not provided, I will send you all work as a zipped file.
